Write a Go test that uses a t.Helper() assertion helper to keep failure line numbers pointing at the caller, testing this function:

```go
// Abs returns the absolute value of x.
func Abs(x int) int {
	if x < 0 {
		return -x
	}
	return x
}
```

response:
